    'A colleague has decided to apply for a promotion and wants to create an action plan. Practice helping them create specific, realistic plans using implementation intentions.',
    '{"name": "Sarah", "role": "colleague", "background": "Experienced advisor ready to apply for specialist role. Motivated but needs help with concrete planning.", "personality_traits": ["motivated", "determined", "practical", "action-oriented"], "tone_spectrum": {"word_complexity": 0.5, "sentence_length": 0.5, "emotional_expressiveness": 0.5, "disclosure_level": 0.5, "response_latency": 0.6, "confidence_level": 0.5}, "starting_tone_position": 0.6, "triggers": ["being told what to do", "dismissiveness", "micromanagement"], "comfort_topics": ["autonomy", "growth", "action", "support"]}'::jsonb,
    '{"start_node_id": "plan_1", "nodes": {"plan_1": {"id": "plan_1", "persona_text": "I''ve decided - I''m going to apply for the Team Lead position. I want to make this happen.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals", "Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_1_0", "option_text": "Great! Here''s what you need to do: update your resume by Friday, schedule a meeting with HR on Monday, and start preparing for the interview next week.", "preview_hint": "Directive approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This jumps immediately to a practitioner-generated plan without exploring their ideas.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_1_1", "option_text": "It sounds like you''re feeling ready to take this step. Would you like to think about what a plan might look like?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.1, "technique_tags": ["reflection", "permission"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - acknowledges readiness, asks permission, and invites their ideas.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2b", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_1_2", "option_text": "Are you sure? This is a big step.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This undermines their expressed readiness rather than supporting it.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2c", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_2a": {"id": "plan_2a", "persona_text": "That sounds intense. I''m not sure I can do all that in that timeframe.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_2a_0", "option_text": "If you''re serious about this position, you need to make the time. These are the steps.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This creates pressure and treats planning as fixed rather than collaborative.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_2a_1", "option_text": "That does sound like a lot. What would feel like a realistic pace for you?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good recovery - validates concern and returns to their planning.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2b", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_2b": {"id": "plan_2b", "persona_text": "Yes, I think so. I was thinking I should update my resume first. Maybe reach out to the current team lead to ask about the role? And prepare some examples of my work?", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_2b_0", "option_text": "Those are thoughtful, specific ideas. Would it be okay to think about when and how these steps might happen?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.1, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "permission"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent - affirms their ideas and seeks permission to make plans concrete.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_3a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_2b_1", "option_text": "That''s a good start, but you''ll need to do more than that.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This devalues what they proposed as insufficient.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_2b_2", "option_text": "You need to also prepare for interviews and talk to HR. Let me add those.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This overrides their plan rather than building on it.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2c", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_2c": {"id": "plan_2c", "persona_text": "Well, when you question me like that, I''m not sure I''m ready after all.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["General"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_2c_0", "option_text": "I didn''t mean to question you. You know you''re ready. Let''s make the plan.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This dismisses the concern without addressing the relationship.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_2c_1", "option_text": "I apologize - I undermined your readiness when you were clear about it. What steps feel right to you?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good - practitioner takes responsibility and returns to collaboration.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2b", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_3a": {"id": "plan_3a", "persona_text": "Sure. I usually have quiet time in the mornings before my shift starts. I could work on my resume then.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Change"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_3a_0", "option_text": "So if it''s a quiet morning before your shift, what could you do specifically on your resume during that time?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["if_then", "open_question"], "competency_links": ["B1"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - uses if-then format to create a concrete implementation intention.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_4a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_3a_1", "option_text": "You should work on it for an hour every morning.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This gives directive advice without eliciting their own ideas.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_4a": {"id": "plan_4a", "persona_text": "I could commit to 30 minutes each morning. I''d start with updating my skills section, then work on my achievements. That seems manageable.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_4a_0", "option_text": "30 minutes each morning on your resume - that''s a specific, realistic commitment. How confident do you feel about sticking with that plan?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "confidence_check"], "competency_links": ["A6", "B1"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Excellent - affirms the plan and checks confidence before finalizing.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_5a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_4a_1", "option_text": "30 minutes isn''t enough. You should do at least an hour.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This changes their plan rather than honoring their realistic assessment.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_5a": {"id": "plan_5a", "persona_text": "Pretty confident. 30 minutes is doable even on busy days. And I can always do more on weekends if I get behind.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_5a_0", "option_text": "High confidence and a built-in flexibility for weekends - that''s a well-thought-out plan. What about reaching out to the current team lead?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "transition"], "competency_links": ["A6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Good - reinforces confidence and moves to next step naturally.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_6a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_5a_1", "option_text": "You should commit to an hour to be safe.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This undermines their confidence-appropriate plan.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_6a": {"id": "plan_6a", "persona_text": "I was thinking I could email her to schedule a quick chat. Maybe next Tuesday during her office hours?", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_6a_0", "option_text": "So your plan is: if it''s Tuesday during office hours, then you''ll have reached out to schedule a chat. When do you think you''ll send that email?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["if_then", "timeline"], "competency_links": ["B1"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - helps make the if-then plan concrete and timeline-specific.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_7a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_6a_1", "option_text": "Tuesday is fine. Send the email today.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This directive approach takes over their timeline.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_2a", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_7a": {"id": "plan_7a", "persona_text": "I can send it this afternoon. I''m usually done with my main tasks by 3pm, so that would work. And if she''s free next Tuesday, great. If not, we can find another time.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [{"id": "cp_plan_7a_0", "option_text": "You''re thinking ahead about both the reminder (3pm when tasks are done) and flexibility (if not Tuesday, another time). That''s a thoughtful approach. How confident do you feel about this overall plan?", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 1, "resistance_impact": -1, "tone_shift": 0.15, "technique_tags": ["affirmation", "confidence_check"], "competency_links": ["A6", "B6"], "feedback": {"immediate": "Perfect - affirms planning and checks confidence before finalizing.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_end_good", "exploration_depth": "surface"}, {"id": "cp_plan_7a_1", "option_text": "You need to be more specific. Set a backup day now.", "preview_hint": "MI-consistent approach", "rapport_impact": 0, "resistance_impact": 0, "tone_shift": 0.0, "technique_tags": ["unknown"], "competency_links": [], "feedback": {"immediate": "This creates unrealistic rigidity rather than flexibility.", "learning_note": "Continue practicing MI techniques to build your coaching skills."}, "next_node_id": "plan_end_poor", "exploration_depth": "surface"}], "is_endpoint": false, "endpoint_type": null}, "plan_end_good": {"id": "plan_end_good", "persona_text": "I feel good about it. Resume work each morning, email this afternoon to schedule a chat. It feels manageable. I have a clear next step.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "neutral_end"}, "plan_end_poor": {"id": "plan_end_poor", "persona_text": "This feels overwhelming. Maybe I''m not as ready as I thought.", "persona_mood": "neutral_uncertain", "themes": ["Goals"], "choice_points": [], "is_endpoint": true, "endpoint_type": "failed_engagement"}}}'::jsonb,
